CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780056672
OL,3,CAdoptee's fight against systemic
OL,4,Cadoption stigma
OL,6,FAfter years of waiting for tests,
OL,7,FChris discovered that he had inherited
OL,8,FMalignant Hyperthermia, a rare genetic
OL,9,Fcondition which causes a life-
OL,10,F threatening reaction to certain
OL,11,Fmedications used in medical settings.
OL,12,FHad Chris required an operation under
OL,13,Fgeneral anaesthetic , he could well
OL,14,Fhave taken a reaction that resulted in
OL,15,Fserious organ damage or death. Whereas
OL,16,Fhad this been known, alternative
OL,17,Fmedications and procedures could have
OL,18,Fbeen administered to remove this risk.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780056672
OL,3,CAdoptee's fight against systemic
OL,4,Cadoption stigma
OL,6,FFor Chris, this was not only a huge
OL,7,Fshock but it got him thinking about
OL,8,Fhow many other people could be
OL,9,Faffected and could he do anything that
OL,10,Fmeant nobody else would have to face a
OL,11,Fsimilar situation.
OL,13,FHe started to reach out to
OL,14,Fpoliticians, social services and the
OL,15,FDept of Health to investigate
OL,16,Fsolutions around operational and
OL,17,Flegislative change that would mean
OL,18,Fcrucial family health history would be
OL,19,Fshared with adoptive families.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780056672
OL,3,CAdoptee's fight against systemic
OL,4,Cadoption stigma
OL,6,FHe joined join the adult adoptee
OL,7,Fadvisory board of the organisation,
OL,8,FAdoption UK and added questions to the
OL,9,F2025 UK-wide research project, the
OL,10,FAdoption Barometer to capture other
OL,11,Fadoptees experience of this entire
OL,12,Fjourney related to accessing medical
OL,13,Fhistories and barriers encountered so
OL,14,Fthat more could be learned about the
OL,15,Fscope of this issue to continue to
OL,16,Flobby and advocate for changes in
OL,17,Fpractice and procedures.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780056672
OL,3,CAdoptee's fight against systemic
OL,4,Cadoption stigma
OL,6,FThere was one thing that Chris said
OL,7,Freally drove home the importance of
OL,8,Fthis experience. The stigma which
OL,9,Fstill surrounds those who are adopted.
OL,10,FThe sense that they should be grateful
OL,11,Ffor their new existence and not
OL,12,Fquestion the processes, the policies
OL,13,Fthat create the adoption process.
OL,15,FBut for Chris, this dysfunction in the
OL,16,Fsystem could have meant the difference
OL,17,Fbetween life and death. So his goal is
OL,18,Fthat he can change the rules so this
OL,19,Fnever happens to any other adopted
OL,20,Fperson again.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
